headline: Buy 4 Discretionary Stocks as Rate Cut Hopes Rise on Easing Inflation
summary: AS, CMPR, PLNT and ABNB stand out as easing November inflation revives rate-cut hopes, lifting consumer discretionary stocks with rising earnings estimates.
